msgid "Aṅguttara Nikāya 6 "
msgstr "Numbered Discourses 6 "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "an6.80:0.2"
msgid "8. Arahattavagga "
msgstr "8. Perfection "

#. HTML: </p><h1>
msgctxt "an6.80:0.3"
msgid "80. Mahantattasutta "
msgstr "80. Greatness "

#. HTML: </h1></div><p>
#. REF: sc1
#. VAR: mahantattaṃ → mahattaṃ (s1-3, km)
msgctxt "an6.80:1.1"
msgid "“Chahi, bhikkhave, dhammehi samannāgato bhikkhu nacirasseva mahantattaṃ vepullattaṃ pāpuṇāti dhammesu. "
msgstr "“Mendicants, a mendicant with six qualities soon acquires great and abundant good qualities. "

msgctxt "an6.80:1.2"
msgid "Katamehi chahi? "
msgstr "What six? "

#. VAR: uttari ca → uttariñca (bj, pts1)
#. VAR: patāreti → pakaroti (mr)
msgctxt "an6.80:1.3"
msgid "Idha, bhikkhave, bhikkhu ālokabahulo ca hoti yogabahulo ca vedabahulo ca asantuṭṭhibahulo ca anikkhittadhuro ca kusalesu dhammesu uttari ca patāreti. "
msgstr "It’s when a mendicant is full of light, full of practice, full of inspiration, and full of eagerness. They don’t slack off when it comes to developing skillful qualities. They reach further. "

msgctxt "an6.80:1.4"
msgid "Imehi kho, bhikkhave, chahi dhammehi samannāgato bhikkhu nacirasseva mahantattaṃ vepullattaṃ pāpuṇāti dhammesū”ti. "
msgstr "A mendicant who has these six qualities soon acquires great and abundant good qualities.” "

#. HTML: </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "an6.80:1.5"
msgid "Chaṭṭhaṃ. "
msgstr ""

